Important: set up a particular style for contracts. Ideas:
* Do not use participants at all. Only dummy participant to connect and get ctc.
* Store all initial state in view
* Store all current global state in view
* Store all local state in view
* Emit events instead of participant interact object stuff
* Maybe never return data in API? Just use events for all output and API for all input?
* Have single view, api, events etc. per contract. So there will be no naming problems. 
* Always use milliseconds?
* Maybe have Common interface for Creator and User participants? It will have ...hasRandom, ...hasLogger, contractStarted(), contractFinished()
